The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Birthday         | june | september     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | helicopter  |

